---
layout: base.njk
title: Newsletter
description: Long-form philosophical writing from the Axiom Society, NSUT.
---

<div class="main">
  <div class="page-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Axiom Writes</p>
    <h1>The Newsletter</h1>
    <p>Essays, reflections, and philosophical musings — written by us, for everyone who thinks.</p>
  </div>

  {% if collections.posts.length %}
    <div class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="post-item">
          <p class="post-date">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </p>
          <h2 class="post-title">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>
          {% if post.data.author %}
            <p class="post-author">by {{ post.data.author }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          {% if post.data.excerpt %}
            <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-read-more">Read essay →</a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p style="color: rgba(26,26,24,0.5); text-align:center; padding: 4rem 0;">
      The first issue is being written. Check back soon.
    </p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
